816
01:13:27.280 --> 01:13:30.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
If they are telling us
to hand them over...

817
01:13:33.520 --> 01:13:35.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
