822
01:14:01.400 --> 01:14:03.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Our role is simply to stay here

823
01:14:03.680 --> 01:14:06.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
