which is there for the park.

824
01:14:06.800 --> 01:14:11.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
If they come here,
we cannot fight against them.

825
01:14:11.800 --> 01:14:15.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
