01:14:31.040 --> 01:14:32.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[speaking French]

831
01:14:45.080 --> 01:14:48.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[driver speaking English]
Press. Press. Press, <i>oui.</i>

832
01:14:48.480 --> 01:14:50.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
