01:15:01.600 --> 01:15:02.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
around the station.

835
01:15:10.400 --> 01:15:12.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
