<i>Many people left Rumangabo.</i>

841
01:15:32.720 --> 01:15:35.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>But, for me,</i>

842
01:15:35.440 --> 01:15:39.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
