843
01:15:44.040 --> 01:15:48.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>You must justify why you are here</i>
<i>on this Earth.</i>

844
01:15:50.160 --> 01:15:56.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Gorillas justify why I am here.</i>

845
01:16:00.840 --> 01:16:02.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[speaking French]
<i>They are my life.</i>

846
01:16:07.200 --> 01:16:09.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>So if it is about dying,</i>

847
01:16:09.080 --> 01:16:13.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I will die for the gorillas.</i>

848
01:16:26.520 --> 01:16:29.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[speaking Swahili]
We've been informed

849
01:16:29.680 --> 01:16:33.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
that the enemy is on his way.

850
01:16:35.080 --> 01:16:37.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You know why we are here.

851
01:16:51.400 --> 01:16:54.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
