the hammer and the anvil.

854
01:17:06.680 --> 01:17:08.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yes.

855
01:17:19.200 --> 01:17:20.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire]

856
