[explosion]

857
01:17:49.120 --> 01:17:50.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[speaking French] They're here.

858
01:17:50.320 --> 01:17:51.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yes, M23 are in Rumangabo.

859
01:17:52.960 --> 01:17:54.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
