01:19:14.880 --> 01:19:16.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire continues]

865
01:19:49.920 --> 01:19:52.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[reporter speaking English]
<i>Until the early hours of Sunday morning,</i>

866
