The M23 rebels are here.

872
01:20:33.080 --> 01:20:34.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
They've entered.

873
01:20:35.040 --> 01:20:39.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
