No more Congolese soldiers. They left.

874
01:20:39.920 --> 01:20:40.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The country is sold.

875
01:20:42.440 --> 01:20:43.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[rebels cheering]

876
01:20:45.600 --> 01:20:46.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[rebels cheering]

877
01:21:41.240 --> 01:21:43.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Bauma speaking English]
<i>It was very difficult for the vet</i>

878
01:21:43.680 --> 01:21:47.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>to come here because of the war.</i>

879
01:21:49.360 --> 01:21:54.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>All the night, yeah, I was with him.</i>

880
01:21:55.480 --> 01:22:00.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>3:00 a.m., he became very weak.</i>

881
01:22:02.000 --> 01:22:05.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>At 5:00 a.m.,</i>

882
01:22:05.960 --> 01:22:11.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
