883
01:22:13.720 --> 01:22:15.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
He left this world.

884
01:22:53.840 --> 01:22:59.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[de Merode] <i>So, our area has now been</i>
<i>overrun by the M23 militias.</i>

885
01:23:00.040 --> 01:23:05.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It has created, for us,</i>
<i>a huge level of uncertainty.</i>

886
01:23:09.040 --> 01:23:10.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>It was impossible for us to leave,</i>

887
01:23:10.960 --> 01:23:13.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>because if we were to leave,</i>
<i>we would lose everything.</i>

888
01:23:13.760 --> 01:23:17.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
