and the wildlife would be at risk,

889
01:23:17.480 --> 01:23:19.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
and we'd lose everything that we've built

890
01:23:19.160 --> 01:23:21.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
over the last few years
to keep this park going.

891
01:23:24.240 --> 01:23:29.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>There was very heavy shelling</i>
<i>and a lot of gunfire.</i>

892
01:23:30.520 --> 01:23:33.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Many people got hurt in the villages.</i>

893
01:23:37.720 --> 01:23:42.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
