<i>and we did our best to help them,</i>

894
01:23:42.760 --> 01:23:47.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>but they were very badly injured,</i>
<i>and some of them died.</i>

895
01:23:48.000 --> 01:23:50.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It was probably
the most violent period we've known.

896
01:24:32.760 --> 01:24:37.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Gouby] <i>There was about 60,000</i>
<i>displaced people living here,</i>

897
01:24:37.320 --> 01:24:39.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
