898
01:24:52.560 --> 01:24:54.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[doctor 1 speaking French]
<i>In the last few days,</i>

899
01:24:54.240 --> 01:24:55.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>we have had many wounded people.</i>

900
01:24:55.800 --> 01:24:57.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
