<i>It's the money that fuels everything.</i>

907
01:25:44.720 --> 01:25:48.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Now we can see the value of that park.

908
01:25:50.280 --> 01:25:52.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
