Yes, we are asking for a percentage.

909
01:25:52.760 --> 01:25:55.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
They cannot exploit oil without us.

910
01:25:55.120 --> 01:25:58.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[John speaking English] <i>It's business,</i>
<i>it's business, and business is business.</i>

911
01:25:58.920 --> 01:26:02.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Lechenault speaking French]
<i>So now there are death threats coming.</i>

912
01:26:02.360 --> 01:26:05.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Death threats, from both sides.</i>

913
01:26:05.160 --> 01:26:09.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Some people are threatening</i>
<i>to kill de Merode.</i>

914
01:26:09.160 --> 01:26:12.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
