comes from him.

916
01:26:14.920 --> 01:26:16.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
They are going to kill him.

917
01:26:19.360 --> 01:26:24.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Gouby speaking English] <i>This company is</i>
<i>operating with the same lack of oversight</i>

918
01:26:24.240 --> 01:26:28.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>that this country has experienced</i>
<i>so many times,</i>

919
01:26:28.120 --> 01:26:31.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>and it's feeding into the conflict.</i>

920
01:26:34.280 --> 01:26:37.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>What I'm really scared about</i>
<i>when this is published,</i>

921
01:26:37.760 --> 01:26:41.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
