<i>and nothing is done about this.</i>

923
01:26:47.160 --> 01:26:52.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>For me, it's not just another</i>
<i>questionable company in Africa...</i>

924
01:26:52.080 --> 01:26:57.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It's a company that has been attacking</i>
<i>one of the only hopes this region has.</i>

925
01:26:58.800 --> 01:27:00.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's intense...

926
01:27:01.640 --> 01:27:04.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
and it can be quite sad... actually.

927
01:27:38.960 --> 01:27:42.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
[de Merode] <i>So the fighting's</i>
<i>been very violent in this area,</i>

928
01:27:42.760 --> 01:27:46.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>and it's meant that</i>
<i>we haven't been able to find the gorillas.</i>

929
01:27:46.160 --> 01:27:49.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>We're extremely worried</i>
<i>about their safety.</i>

930
01:27:51.960 --> 01:27:54.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Now, finally, we've been able to get back.</i>

